BS/AP May 12, 2017, 4:42 PM, Chinese investors spent $24B on \"golden visas\" in U.S. and elsewhere, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/golden-visas-chinese-investors-24-billion-in-u-s-and-elsewhere/\">[1]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Almeida-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Almeida_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Henrique Almeida, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-01-20/chinese-property-buyers-stuck-in-portugal-s-golden-visa-limbo\">Chinese Stuck in Portugal's Visa Limbo</a>, Bloomberg News (January 20, 2016).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Where is the cheapest place to buy citizenship?, By Kim Gittleson BBC reporter, New York, 4 June 2014, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-27674135\">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-27674135</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Canada kills investor visa popular with Chinese, by Sophia Yan, March 25, 2014: 2:21 AM ET , CNN, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://money.cnn.com/2014/02/12/news/canada-chinese-immigration/index.html\">[2]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Buying their way in, Economist 22 november 2014 <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"https://www.economist.com/news/europe/21633854-schemes-effect-sell-visas-rich-foreigners-come-under-fire-buying-their-way\">[3]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text